# SPDX-License-Identifier: MIT
#
# AGEZT - Pure Go Project
#
# This file explicitly disables CGO for this entire project.
# CGO_ENABLED=0 is set globally for this project.
#
# What this means:
# - All builds use pure Go (no C dependencies)
# - No external C libraries required
# - Cross-compilation works out of the box
# - Race detector is NOT available (requires CGO)
#
# To run tests with race detector:
#   CGO_ENABLED=1 go test -race ./...
#   (requires GCC to be installed)
#
# Project: https://github.com/agezt/agezt
# Pure Go: https://purego.doc
